name: Kunio-kun no Dodge Ball - Zenin Shuugou! [SNES]
description: (GOAL 3) Kunio-kun no Nekketsu Soccer League (くにおくんの熱血サッカーリーグ) is a Soccer video game for the Family Computer, both developed and published by Technōs Japan released on 1993. It is a direct sequel to the Nekketsu Kōkō Dodgeball-bu: Soccer Hen, not international version of Nintendo World Cup.
